high_descs: Turn to the right, then the left. Turn left to face the white table on the left side.
Pick up the bread from the center of the table.
Carry the bread and turn left, then turn right past the table. Turn left and locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bread inside. Shut the door and then open it. Take out the bread and shut the door.
Hold the bread and turn to the left. Move to the counter.
Place the bread on the counter, on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread and move it to the counter.

high_descs: Move around to the right side of the table in front of you, turn left to face the kettle on the right side of the table.
Pick up the bread on the table.
Turn left, bring the bread to the fridge across the room to the right.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Bring the chilled bread to the left, to the counter with the coffee machine.
Put the chilled bread on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bread on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
